data.text:
Kahani & Kunal Merchant with special guest Mowgli

Indo Warehouse Australia Tour 2024 Indo Warehouse is a New York based collective, record label and experiential series that showcases the beauty of South Asian culture, music, and rhythm within the global language of house and techno. Making their Australian debut, label heads Kahani & Kunal Merchant are bringing their distinct ‘Indo House’ sounds to Liberty Hall this June. Renowned for their sense of community & connection, 2023 saw a string of sold out Indo Warehouse shows across North America, London, India, and a debut show at the globally recognised Amsterdam Dance Event. Join us for the Australian debut of Indo Warehouse this June.
